01:25:38.875 --> 01:25:44.594
no problem of any kind, to have a son
like Him,

01:25:45.819 --> 01:25:50.977
completely obedient, absolutely 100%
obedience and humility

01:25:51.178 --> 01:25:56.128
and understanding of Your Being.

01:25:58.745 --> 01:26:01.875
No problems.

01:26:03.940 --> 01:26:08.134
You are all My sons too, and made
after Him,

01:26:08.335 --> 01:26:12.719
