01:45:33.303 --> 01:45:36.559
Letter you give up.

01:45:56.812 --> 01:46:00.241
This is ghee?
Yogini: Yes, Mother.

01:46:00.442 --> 01:46:05.425
Shri Mataji: This is ghee! So much!
Out of proportion it is, I mean.

01:46:05.626 --> 01:46:09.071
It’s too much softening.

01:46:11.502 --> 01:46:16.268
All right, give Me little bit now, some.
Just a wee bit.

01:46:16.469 --> 01:46:21.473
As it is you all have liver, so you don’t
need ghee.

01:46:24.506 --> 01:46:26.827
It’s all right.

01:46:29.193 --> 01:46:32.087
Now pour some water.

01:46:36.905 --> 01:46:41.017
Good for cleaning the nose of all
the people who have sinus…

01:46:41.218 --> 01:46:45.646
the ghee, but not for eating, eh?

01:46:57.326 --> 01:47:01.010
Now. Little bit now of another thing,
whatever it is.

01:47:17.051 --> 01:47:19.902
Put the whole thing.

01:47:26.253 --> 01:47:29.310
Again some water.

01:47:42.024 --> 01:47:44.215
Now.

01:47:47.777 --> 01:47:51.041
Milk has to be more. Madhu,
madhu,

01:47:51.242 --> 01:47:54.488
you get madhu first, madhu means…

01:47:54.903 --> 01:47:58.428
Milk will be more than this. Yes.

01:48:25.457 --> 01:48:28.626
Gavin: Shall I put milk next?

01:48:28.827 --> 01:48:32.742
Shri Mataji: Yes, milk, then. And more
milk than…

01:48:38.369 --> 01:48:42.587
Gavin: …sugar.
Shri Mataji: Yes.

01:48:53.801 --> 01:48:56.902
Milk. Need for more milk, I think.

01:49:16.653 --> 01:49:21.356
More. Here.

01:49:23.709 --> 01:49:26.717
Yes, it’s all right.

01:49:43.175 --> 01:49:46.177
Not too much sugar.

01:50:07.430 --> 01:50:11.298
Not to feel guilty, for Heaven’s sake.

01:50:13.355 --> 01:50:17.139
Not to feel guilty at all, left -
left Vishuddhi catching.

01:50:17.340 --> 01:50:20.693
Don’t think! In My presence you are
not supposed to think at all.

01:50:20.894 --> 01:50:25.776
Just don’t think. Don’t feel guilty.

01:50:27.103 --> 01:50:33.148
Catching, still.
[Aside] Good, thank you.

01:50:40.597 --> 01:50:44.376
Yogi: She’s posing!
Shri Mataji: She’s posing!

01:50:54.703 --> 01:51:00.538
Look at her. Wrapped up in the sari.

01:51:01.627 --> 01:51:04.575
Fitting in great, herself [unclear].

01:51:05.489 --> 01:51:08.842
Gavin: Just matches her eyes.
Shri Mataji: Eh?

01:51:09.043 --> 01:51:14.409
Gavin: The sari just matches her eyes.
Shri Mataji: You see? Just see [indistinct].

01:51:17.443 --> 01:51:20.903
It’s a dignified thing, you know,
sari is very dignified.

01:51:21.104 --> 01:51:24.629
Now. All right.

01:51:44.835 --> 01:51:49.392
Very nice people. Very sensible.

01:51:54.084 --> 01:51:58.274
Gavin, in your list you must put this also.

01:52:00.141 --> 01:52:04.720
If you tell this list to Me, there,
who is coming gives you.

01:52:04.921 --> 01:52:08.519
Who are coming to India out of you?

01:52:12.131 --> 01:52:14.397
Here?

01:52:23.445 --> 01:52:28.537
Now, those who are coming should
get this list

01:52:28.738 --> 01:52:35.313
of a few things that you need,
essential ones.

01:52:35.514 --> 01:52:40.310
I don’t find that thing with which you used
to give Me water, is it here or not?

01:52:40.511 --> 01:52:42.807
With the spoon and all that.

01:52:43.008 --> 01:52:45.142
Gavin: I must check it with Marcus
afterwards. Shri Mataji: Marcus?

01:52:45.343 --> 01:52:47.851
Marcus: Yes, Mother.
Shri Mataji: You’ve got that spoon and…

01:52:48.052 --> 01:52:51.131
Marcus: Yes, Mother. Shri Mataji: That
you have got. Marcus: Yes.

01:52:52.277 --> 01:52:56.898
Shri Mataji: All right [speaks aside in a
low voice. Sounds like: there’s the spoon].

01:53:08.464 --> 01:53:13.202
This one is very good because it is not
hard wood.

01:55:13.121 --> 01:55:16.615
Yogi: Christmas… [indistinct].

01:55:41.089 --> 01:55:47.980
Shri Mataji: Now, just put some red
on my hand. Red [Kumkum? Unclear]

01:55:52.964 --> 01:55:57.816
Shri Mataji: I will. Gavin: Our Mother,
You are the Counsellor

01:55:58.017 --> 01:56:02.474
who was promised by Christ.
Shri Mataji: I am.

01:56:02.675 --> 01:56:06.829
Gavin: You make us become our
own knowledge.

01:56:09.830 --> 01:56:14.925
Our Mother, You are the Redeemer,
who was promised by Christ.

01:56:16.523 --> 01:56:19.946
You have given us our second birth.

01:56:23.168 --> 01:56:30.535
Our Mother, You are the fulfillment
of every prophecy and every prayer.

01:56:32.903 --> 01:56:35.693
Our Mother, You are the wholesomeness,

01:56:35.894 --> 01:56:40.167
by which all wrongs are cleansed.

01:56:43.421 --> 01:56:47.609
Our Mother, You are the right
discrimination

01:56:47.810 --> 01:56:52.204
by which we have received enlightenment.

01:56:55.579 --> 01:56:58.768
Our Mother, You are the integration,

01:56:58.969 --> 01:57:04.232
by You God’s whole creation has been
threaded together.

01:57:09.741 --> 01:57:13.836
We bow to You who are auspiciousness;

01:57:18.710 --> 01:57:22.163
we praise You who are Love;

01:57:24.522 --> 01:57:29.056
we give thanks to You who are compassion;

01:57:31.176 --> 01:57:41.147
we prostrate before You who are all-knowing,
all-seeing and all-forgiving.

01:57:43.043 --> 01:57:45.882
We are Your children:

01:57:47.797 --> 01:57:51.358
let us never be separated from You,

01:57:51.559 --> 01:57:57.197
whether by Your illusion, or by our
own limitations.

01:57:59.150 --> 01:58:02.607
Give us strength of Spirit

01:58:05.918 --> 01:58:12.329
and to the world give peace. Aum.

01:58:13.363 --> 01:58:15.827
Yogis: Amen.

01:58:42.961 --> 01:58:49.112
Shri Mataji: Let your life be fragrant
by My blessings,

01:58:52.876 --> 01:58:55.747
by My love,

01:58:58.715 --> 01:59:02.071
by My concern,

01:59:02.882 --> 01:59:06.788
and the pride that I have for you all.

01:59:33.570 --> 01:59:36.399
May God bless you.

01:59:42.526 --> 01:59:46.203
Yogini: … and it’s called “Mother God”.
Shri Mataji: Who?

01:59:46.404 --> 01:59:52.117
Yogini: It’s called “Mother God”. Shri
Mataji: “Mother God”. Yogini: “Mother God”.

02:02:55.773 --> 02:02:58.027
Shri Mataji: Oh.

02:03:17.755 --> 02:03:23.572
Sang [you?] with such a heart. Everybody
was, everybody’s heart was singing with you.

02:03:23.773 --> 02:03:28.177
Thank you very much. May God bless you.

02:03:34.809 --> 02:03:37.442
These songs should be recorded
and should be sent to India.

02:03:37.643 --> 02:03:42.073
They would be very happy, you see,
to have these songs.

02:03:51.048 --> 02:03:53.277
Very beautiful. Who wrote it?
Yogini: Hugo wrote it, Mother.

02:03:53.518 --> 02:03:56.526
Shri Mataji: Eh? Yogini: Hugo wrote it.
Shri Mataji: Hugo. Yogini: Hugo did that.

02:03:56.727 --> 02:04:00.615
Shri Mataji: Congratulations.
Give him a hand.

02:04:16.080 --> 02:04:18.842
Beautiful.

02:04:19.779 --> 02:04:22.069
Integration is so important, you see.

02:04:22.270 --> 02:04:24.888
Somebody has to write, somebody
has to compose,

02:04:25.089 --> 02:04:28.674
somebody has to sing and somebody
has to listen.
